Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC operates as an investment management company. The Company offers asset management, equities, fundamental research, investment strategies, financial planning, and advisory services. Legion Partners Asset Management serves customers in the State of California.




