Investment company Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC buys Banc of California Inc, Ciber Inc, Trecora Resources, sells 1347 Property Insurance Holdings Inc, Key Technology Inc during the 3-months ended 2017-03-31, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC. As of 2017-03-31, Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC owns 11 stocks with a total value of $166 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: TREC, Added Positions: BANC, FSTR, CBRIQ, CHEF, Reduced Positions: SHOR, Sold Out: PIH, KTEC, Warning! GuruFocus has detected 4 Warning Signs with BANC. Click here to check it out. 
