dings in  1347 Property Insurance Holdings Inc.  The sale prices were between $6.5 and $8.1, with an estimated average price of $7.18. Sold Out: Key Technology Inc (KTEC)Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC sold out the holdings in  Key Technology Inc.  The sale prices were between $11.71 and $13.85, with an estimated average price of $12.79. Here is the complete portfolio of Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC. Also check out:
