The Site may contain links to websites controlled or offered by third parties. Legion Partners hereby disclaims all liability for any and all data, information, materials, products or services posted or offered at any of the third party sites linked to the Site ("Linked Website"). The Linked Websites are provided merely as a convenience and Legion Partners shall not be responsible or liable, directly or indirectly, for any loss, damage, claims, costs and expenses caused or alleged to be caused by or in connection with access to, use of or reliance on a Linked Website. By having a Linked Website, Legion Partners does not recommend, sponsor or endorse any content, opinions, advice, products or services offered or posted at that Linked Website. You agree that Legion Partners is not responsible for the availability or reliability of such Linked Websites or for the quality or failure of any products or services available or advertised on such Linked Websites. You acknowledge that Legion Partners shall not be responsible for the accuracy, reliability, completeness, truthfulness, currency, copyright or trademark compliance, legality or decency of any information, data or materials contained in a Linked Website, nor any link contained in a Linked Website. You are fully responsible for viewing and following the terms of use and privacy statements at the Linked Websites.  
7. Third Party Information.
From time to time, information, including news, company reports and other data, prepared by third parties may appear on the Site. You acknowledge and agree that such third party information is for your personal use only and that you will not retransmit or republish it in any form. You acknowledge that any such third party information is obtained from sources believed to be reliable, and is provided solely on a best efforts basis for your convenience, and that no representations, warranties or guarantees are made by Legion Partners or any provider of such third party information as to the accuracy, completeness, timeliness or correct sequencing thereof. Third party information has been prepared as of the date(s) indicated and may become unreliable because of subsequent market or economic circumstances. Neither Legion Partners nor the provider of such information is under any obligation to update such information or continue to offer such information.
