The information contained on the Site was prepared by Legion partners.  The information is believed by Legion partners to be reliable and has been obtained from public sources believed to be reliable. Legion partners makes no representation or warranty, express or implied, as to the fairness, accuracy, completeness or correctness of such information, nor does Legion partners or any of its affiliates accept any liability arising from its use. Opinions, estimates and projections on the Site constitute the current judgment of Legion partners and are subject to change without notice. Legion partners has no obligation to update, modify or amend the information on the Site or to otherwise notify you in the event that any matter stated on the Site, or any opinion, projection, forecast or estimate set forth herein, changes or subsequently becomes inaccurate.

The information contained on the Site pertaining to any private investment fund does not constitute an offer to purchase, sell or exchange shares or interests issued by such fund nor any other securities.  Your eligibility to invest in any private investment fund is subject to final determination by Legion partners and/or its affiliate(s). No private investment fund and none of the interests or shares offered by any private investment fund have been registered under the federal securities laws of the United States, the securities laws of any state, or the laws of any other jurisdiction. No securities transactions may take place on the Site. Neither Legion partners nor any of its affiliates recommends or solicits any investment by users of the Site.

Investments in any private investment fund are speculative and involve a high degree of risk. You could lose all or a substantial amount of your investment in a private investment fund. The risks disclosed in the Site do not include all of the risks and other significant considerations of an investment in a private investment fund.  You should carefully read a private investment fund’s offering materials for specific risks and other important information regarding such fund before investing in the fund. Prior to making any investment decision or hiring any investment manager, you should consult with a professional financial, legal and tax adviser to assist in due diligence to determine the appropriateness of the risk associated with a particular investment. Past performance is not indicative of future results.

The information contained on the Site provided herein shall not form the primary basis of any investment decision. Each investor should independently confirm such information, obtain any other information deemed relevant to an investment decision and consult with the investor’s own advisers, as the investor deems necessary. Investors should not treat these materials as advice in relation to legal, taxation or investment matters. The information contained on the Site is provided for informational purposes only.
